Dialogue: 4,0:00:06.19,0:00:12.04,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,《大室家 dear sisters》原創廣播劇 花子篇
Dialogue: 4,0:00:13.05,0:00:16.15,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,《捉蟲對決在烏龍麵後》
Dialogue: 4,0:00:25.29,0:00:27.47,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,今天要用捉蟲來決勝負喔
Dialogue: 4,0:00:28.12,0:00:29.83,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,捉蟲
Dialogue: 4,0:00:30.35,0:00:31.81,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,蘋果
Dialogue: 4,0:00:32.06,0:00:32.92,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,大猩猩
Dialogue: 4,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.10,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,沒說是詞語接龍啊
Dialogue: 4,0:00:35.10,0:00:38.28,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 我還挺怕蟲子的
Dialogue: 4,0:00:38.28,0:00:40.70,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,又在說什麼決勝負
Dialogue: 4,0:00:42.04,0:00:45.86,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,這樣的話 就直接算岬贏了喔
Dialogue: 4,0:00:46.21,0:00:47.26,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,老鼠
Dialogue: 4,0:00:49.22,0:00:51.57,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,密西西比彩龜
Dialogue: 4,0:00:51.57,0:00:52.60,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,哈密瓜汽水
Dialogue: 4,0:00:52.60,0:00:55.57,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,都說了不是詞語接龍啊
Dialogue: 4,0:00:55.57,0:00:56.73,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,甜甜圈
Dialogue: 4,0:00:56.73,0:00:58.21,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,柿餅
Dialogue: 4,0:00:58.43,0:01:00.32,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,吉利支丹大名
Dialogue: 4,0:01:04.33,0:01:05.23,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,烏龍麵
Dialogue: 4,0:01:06.63,0:01:09.07,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,詞語接龍算岬子輸了
Dialogue: 4,0:01:16.98,0:01:18.56,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,也還是來捉蟲子了
Dialogue: 4,0:01:18.56,0:01:21.78,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,捉到的蟲子最大的人算贏喔
Dialogue: 4,0:01:24.16,0:01:26.96,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,太熱了 感覺蟲子都沒多少了
Dialogue: 4,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.72,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,還是回去吧
Dialogue: 4,0:01:28.97,0:01:31.56,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,蟬倒是有好多
Dialogue: 4,0:01:31.84,0:01:33.60,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,蟬不行
Dialogue: 4,0:01:33.60,0:01:34.76,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 4,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.79,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,姐姐說過
Dialogue: 4,0:01:37.13,0:01:40.03,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,蟬在土地裡待了好幾年
Dialogue: 4,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.08,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,等到終於能出來了
Dialogue: 4,0:01:42.31,0:01:44.29,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,卻又短短兩週就會死掉
Dialogue: 4,0:01:44.55,0:01:47.43,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,好…好可憐
Dialogue: 4,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.96,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,也不至於哭吧
Dialogue: 4,0:01:51.22,0:01:55.70,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,那…那就不捉蟬了吧
Dialogue: 4,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.61,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,蟬會在土地裡待多少年呢
Dialogue: 4,0:01:58.61,0:02:00.68,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,姐姐說是三年左右
Dialogue: 4,0:02:00.89,0:02:05.77,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,岬子還在穿尿布的時候就在土裡了
Dialogue: 4,0:02:05.77,0:02:09.69,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,人家三年前已經不穿尿不濕了啦
Dialogue: 4,0:02:11.71,0:02:14.24,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,哇 蟬掉下來了
Dialogue: 4,0:02:14.24,0:02:18.26,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,已…已經過了兩週 死掉了嗎
Dialogue: 4,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.19,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,它度過了一段美好的蟬生嗎
Dialogue: 4,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.47,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,大家一起合上手
Dialogue: 4,0:02:23.47,0:02:26.30,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,祈禱它能去到天堂吧
Dialogue: 4,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.63,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,這不是還活著嗎
Dialogue: 4,0:02:42.49,0:02:46.18,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,沒想到蟬還挺頑強的呢
Dialogue: 4,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.57,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,要捉的話 還是甲蟲什麼的吧
Dialogue: 4,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.45,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,該怎麼捉呢
Dialogue: 4,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.39,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,用蜂蜜引誘它們過來
Dialogue: 4,0:02:56.39,0:02:58.18,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,竟然帶蜂蜜了
Dialogue: 4,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.22,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,不愧是花子大小姐
Dialogue: 4,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.89,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 4,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.36,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,別吃啊
Dialogue: 4,0:03:06.35,0:03:10.32,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,蜂蜜的話 岬也帶著呢
Dialogue: 4,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.62,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,蟲子 來了
Dialogue: 4,0:03:18.21,0:03:21.81,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,心把捉蟲的網罩到岬的頭上了
Dialogue: 4,0:03:21.81,0:03:24.59,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,岬子可不是蟲子喔 心
Dialogue: 4,0:03:27.63,0:03:30.76,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,剛才蟲子就在岬子的頭上喔
Dialogue: 4,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.54,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,看 這不是嗎
Dialogue: 4,0:03:36.09,0:03:38.59,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,這麼亂動很危險的
Dialogue: 4,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.20,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,會…會摔倒的
Dialogue: 4,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.62,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,岬子也害怕蟲子嗎
Dialogue: 4,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.97,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,身上還有隻青蟲
Dialogue: 4,0:03:48.08,0:03:52.05,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,害怕的話 為什麼還要用捉蟲決勝負
Dialogue: 4,0:03:59.22,0:04:03.06,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,只是有點怕軟乎乎的蟲子而已
Dialogue: 4,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.54,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,硬的蟲子才沒事呢
Dialogue: 4,0:04:05.54,0:04:07.71,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,倒不如說還挺喜歡呢
Dialogue: 4,0:04:07.71,0:04:09.26,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,臭蟲什麼的呢
Dialogue: 4,0:04:09.26,0:04:12.07,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,臭蟲雖然硬但也不行
Dialogue: 4,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.63,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,那邊好像有個什麼硬硬的東西
Dialogue: 4,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.99,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,交給岬吧
Dialogue: 4,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.55,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,太好了 我抓到了
Dialogue: 4,0:04:28.13,0:04:31.46,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,是金龜子 還挺大的
Dialogue: 4,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.31,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,我帶尺來了 量一下吧
Dialogue: 4,0:04:34.31,0:04:35.76,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,借我用一下
Dialogue: 4,0:04:41.30,0:04:44.00,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,有35公分長
Dialogue: 4,0:04:44.00,0:04:46.20,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,才沒有這麼大的金龜子呢
Dialogue: 4,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.73,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,有的話還挺恐怖的
Dialogue: 4,0:04:47.96,0:04:50.15,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,明明是35毫米
Dialogue: 4,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.16,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,花子也找到了
Dialogue: 4,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.42,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 4,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.43,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,看 是個甲蟲
Dialogue: 4,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.73,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 4,0:05:04.73,0:05:07.16,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,不愧是花子大小姐
Dialogue: 4,0:05:07.16,0:05:10.24,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,比岬子的金龜子大了一倍
Dialogue: 4,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.88,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,是花子大小姐贏了呢
Dialogue: 4,0:05:13.13,0:05:16.72,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,還…還沒決出勝負呢
Dialogue: 4,0:05:16.72,0:05:19.85,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,不是岬子你說按大小決勝負的嗎
Dialogue: 4,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.01,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,真是幼稚
Dialogue: 4,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.55,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,才不是越大越好呢
Dialogue: 4,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.26,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,不比大小的話 那比什麼呢
Dialogue: 4,0:05:27.48,0:05:29.31,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,比蟲子的內在喔
Dialogue: 4,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.22,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,內在？
Dialogue: 4,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.05,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,解剖…
Dialogue: 4,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.91,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,別說得這麼嚇人
Dialogue: 4,0:05:37.21,0:05:40.23,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,蟲…蟲子的內在是什麼
Dialogue: 4,0:05:40.60,0:05:44.43,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,比如說 聰不聰明和性格好不好
Dialogue: 4,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.17,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,還有前途什麼的
Dialogue: 4,0:05:46.17,0:05:49.89,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,還有…年收入？
Dialogue: 4,0:05:50.18,0:05:52.54,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,什麼年收入啊
Dialogue: 4,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.51,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,心也找到了
Dialogue: 4,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.77,Text_Mirai_CN,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 4,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.49,Text_Kokoro_CN,,0,0,0,,是長戟大兜蟲
Dialogue: 4,0:06:04.74,0:06:07.06,Text_Misaki_CN,,0,0,0,,它怎麼這麼大啊
Dialogue: 4,0:06:07.83,0:06:11.38,Text_Hanako_CN,,0,0,0,,後山怎麼會有這種蟲子啊
